'''Yankee Dime''', a rarely-used slang term found in the [[American South]] to indicate a kiss, for example; "If you bring me a glass of sweet, iced tea, I will give you a Yankee Dime." Sometimes the term refers to an insincere kiss, or it can, in some cases, just be a joking matter.
<br>
